ardour: ardour (Multichannel Digital Audio Workstation)
ardour:
ardour: Ardour is a multichannel hard disk recorder (HDR) and digital audio
ardour: workstation (DAW). It is capable of simultaneous recording 24 or more
ardour: channels of 32 bit audio at 48kHz. Ardour is intended to function as
ardour: a "professional" HDR system, replacing dedicated hardware solutions
ardour: such as the Mackie HDR, the Tascam 2424 and more traditional tape
ardour: systems like the Alesis ADAT series.
ardour: http://ardour.org
